Police in Thailand opened fire on a car driven by an ` crazy ' American tourist after she drove the wrong way down a busy road and crashed into 13 vehicles , injuring two people .
The 29-year-old woman was chased by police through the Pattaya region for 30 minutes before they shot out three wheels of her car .
The blonde woman was then bundled into a police car - to protect her from an angry mob that had formed in the wake of the carnage .